OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FContent warning: This report contains
OL,7,Fdetails that some readers may find
OL,8,Fupsetting
OL,10,FA jury has heard a woman describe
OL,11,Fdetails of the moment she alleges she
OL,12,Fwas raped as a child by Sir Jeffrey
OL,13,FDonaldson.
OL,15,FThe complainant told of hearing the
OL,16,Fformer DUP leader's "heavy breathing"
OL,17,Fduring the alleged sexual assault.
