OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1780434670
OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FA police interview with a second
OL,7,Falleged victim in Donaldson's sexual
OL,8,Foffences trial has been played at
OL,9,FNewry Crown Court.
OL,11,FThe ex-MP, 63, has pleaded not guilty
OL,12,Fto 18 alleged offences.
OL,14,FThe charges span a time period between
OL,15,F1985 and 2008 involving two alleged
OL,16,Fvictims.
OL,18,FEleanor Donaldson denies several
OL,19,Fcharges of aiding and abetting her
OL,20,Fhusband's alleged offending.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
