OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FShe is facing a trial of the facts.
OL,8,FComplainant B, one of the two alleged
OL,9,Fvictims, was not in the courtroom, but
OL,10,Fappeared via a video link.
OL,12,FHer achieving best evidence interview
OL,13,Fwith police was played to the jury of
OL,14,Fseven men and five women on Tuesday
OL,15,Fmorning.
OL,17,FJeffrey Donaldson sat in the dock at
OL,18,Fthe rear of the courtroom, while the
OL,19,Finterview, which was recorded in March
OL,20,F2024, was played.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
