OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FIn the interview the complainant said
OL,7,Fthat growing up she was "sexually
OL,8,Fabused by an adult".
OL,10,FShe said she particularly remembered
OL,11,Ftwo incidents.
OL,13,FThe woman frequently became emotional
OL,14,Fduring the interview.
OL,16,FIn the first, she said it occurred
OL,17,Fwhen she was of primary school age.
OL,18,FShe claimed, Donaldson had put his
OL,19,Fhands down her underwear and then
OL,20,Fsexually assaulted her.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
