OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FShe said the second incident occurred
OL,7,Fwhen she was slightly older when, she
OL,8,Fsaid, Donaldson "lifted up my top" and
OL,9,Ftouched her breasts.
OL,11,FAsked by a police officer if there
OL,12,Fwere other incidents, she said she
OL,13,Fremembered "his hands down my pants a
OL,14,Flot".
OL,16,FShe said: "I remember I couldn't tell
OL,17,Fanybody, I remember telling my
OL,18,Fimaginary friend."
OL,26,@pD@QOUpD@bO]uD@LOUvD@DO]xD@KOUzD@RO]
