OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FAsked by police for the name of her
OL,7,Falleged abuser, she said "Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson MP".
OL,10,FRecalling the alleged rape, she said:
OL,11,F"I kept thinking it is OK, it will be
OL,12,Fover soon... I remember hearing his
OL,13,Fbreathing."
OL,15,FThe complainant then said she felt
OL,16,F"something different" and said that
OL,17,FDonaldson was on top of her, but
OL,18,Fslightly to the right.
OL,20,FShe then said he sexually assaulted
OL,21,Fher.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUpD@MO]sD@AOUuD@KO]xD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
