OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson sexual offences
OL,4,Ctrial hears from second alleged victim
OL,6,FThe complainant said: "I don't know if
OL,7,Fit continued or if that was it."
OL,9,FShe added: "I just kept my eyes
OL,10,Fclosed."
OL,12,FShe said: "I just remember hearing his
OL,13,Fheavy breathing."
OL,15,FThe trial continues.
OL,17,FJeffrey Donaldson, a former long-
OL,18,Fstanding MP for Lagan Valley, was
OL,19,Farrested and charged at the end of
OL,20,FMarch 2024.
OL,26,@nD@WOUoD@`O]qD@LOUrD@HO]tD@KOUuD@QO]
